<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1111665-how-historically-accurate-is-this-book">How historically accurate is this book? Will I learn anything from it, or is it more of a fun read?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1111665'><a id="like_count_community_question_1111665" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1111665?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F5368.Forever_Amber">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1111665-how-historically-accurate-is-this-book">4 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1111665-how-historically-accurate-is-this-book">See all 3 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
