<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1118052-my-question-do-you-think-someone-was">My question: do you think someone was actually paid to proofread this book? When I am finding books via my kindle, and it is a free book; I don&#39;t expect perfection..but this book was so riddled with typos it just at times took me right out of that &quot;space&quot; we avid readers zone out into. I felt like I should have been paid for all the times I ended up deciding to stop, hit the typo button and fill out the correction.</a>
