            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4674014-marquise?shelf=ending-is-a-big-stunner">ending-is-a-big-stunner</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4674014-marquise?shelf=insanely-badass-moment">insanely-badass-moment</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4674014-marquise?shelf=5-stars">5-stars</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4674014-marquise?shelf=historical-setting-1600s">historical-setting-1600s</a>, 
